translation.id: You must notify AREA in writing within 15 days of receiving the shipment of any discrepancies in the shipment, such as the specifications, quantity, damage, etc. (“Discrepancy”).
translation.FR: Vous devez aviser AREA par écrit dans les 15 jours suivant la réception du colis de divergence dans le transport, telles que le cahier des charges , la quantité, dommages , etc (“Discordance”) .

translations.translation: You must notify AREA in writing within 15 days of receiving the shipment of any discrepancies in the shipment, such as the specifications, quantity, damage, etc. (“Discrepancy”).

translation.id: If you notify Area within 15 days of receiving the shipment of a Discrepancy, Area will request its distributor to correct the Discrepancy and the distributor will pay the shipping charges to replace the defective or non-conforming products.
translation.FR: Si vous informez Area dans les 15 jours suivant la réception de l'envoi de divergence , Area va demander à son distributeur pour corriger l'écart et le distributeur paiera les frais de transport pour remplacer les produits défectueux ou non conformes .

translations.translation: If you notify Area within 15 days of receiving the shipment of a Discrepancy, Area will request its distributor to correct the Discrepancy and the distributor will pay the shipping charges to replace the defective or non-conforming products.
